<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 18:08:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>这些是周五从哈马斯囚禁中获释的以色列妇女和儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-women-and-children-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-friday/0000018c-0178-d4d0-addf-47febba50000</link><description>49 天前，以色列人质在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击期间从尼尔奥兹基布兹被绑架，并被拖到加沙，作为加沙战争期间有限停火协议的一部分，这些人质被释放</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 17:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-women-and-children-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-friday/0000018c-0178-d4d0-addf-47febba50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列人如此反对与哈马斯的战争停火？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-are-israelis-so-averse-to-a-cease-fire-in-the-war-with-hamas/0000018c-01f0-d12e-a1fc-71f5ccdc0000</link><description>与普遍观点相反，停止枪击的协议在战场之外发挥着重要作用。难怪政府和军队都想方设法避免它</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 16:25:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-are-israelis-so-averse-to-a-cease-fire-in-the-war-with-hamas/0000018c-01f0-d12e-a1fc-71f5ccdc0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这位种族冲突问题顶级专家对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人抱有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-this-top-expert-on-ethnic-conflicts-has-hope-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-0191-dca2-a9fd-659bf8590000</link><description>世界民族政治冲突权威社会学家、政治哲学家安德烈亚斯·维默 (Andreas Wimmer) 表示，赢得战争的方法是征服敌人，但结束冲突的方法是让对手分享权力地位</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 15:26:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-this-top-expert-on-ethnic-conflicts-has-hope-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-0191-dca2-a9fd-659bf8590000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火满足了伊朗和美国利益的融合</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/the-cease-fire-in-gaza-feeds-a-confluence-of-iranian-and-american-interests/0000018c-00e1-de0a-a18e-06f5e9d90000</link><description>伊朗和美国都明白，加沙战争 — — 特别是以色列和黎巴嫩边境的冲突 — — 可能会将整个地区拖入一场战争，迫使两国直接交战。对伊朗而言，停火可能是恢复现状的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 11:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/the-cease-fire-in-gaza-feeds-a-confluence-of-iranian-and-american-interests/0000018c-00e1-de0a-a18e-06f5e9d90000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙领导人掌权，哈马斯海外官员认为权力减弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-abroad-see-power-wane-as-gazan-leaders-take-control/0000018c-00ce-d99b-a7ee-1dde271f0000</link><description>最近在卡塔尔会见哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和其他高级官员的阿拉伯外交官表示，每一项有关该组织未来或人质交易的提议或讨论都会得到这样的答案：“我们将看看他们在加沙说什么”</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 10:59:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-abroad-see-power-wane-as-gazan-leaders-take-control/0000018c-00ce-d99b-a7ee-1dde271f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境沿线的居民全副武装，焦虑不安，正在为最坏的情况做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</link><description>战争爆发以来，以色列边境居民的安全感受到严重动摇。曾经享受平静生活和田园风光的人们现在正在武装自己，想知道敌人需要多长时间才能突破脆弱的栅栏</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 05:17:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火期间，13名以色列人质从哈马斯手中获释返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</link><description>第一批被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质抵达以色列 ■ 为期四天的停火于当地时间周五上午 7 点生效 ■ 卡塔尔-埃及与哈马斯达成的另一项调解协议中释放了 11 名人质 ■ 载有人道主义援助的卡车进入加沙通过拉法过境点通往埃及 ■ 以色列监狱管理局开始释放巴勒斯坦囚犯 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀，236 名人质在加沙地带被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列进入加沙休战，内塔尼亚胡继续对国防机构发动战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道以色列国防军将因摧毁加沙而获得赞誉，就像他明白人质交易将帮助他走出政治深渊一样。与此同时，极右翼分子伊塔马尔·本-格维尔正在制定一项退出执政联盟的战略</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</guid></item><item><title>随着第一批人质即将获释，以色列已经在计划下一阶段的加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</link><description>战斗的暂停将使以色列国防军能够在加沙地带南部组织新的进攻，这可能需要几个月的时间。受西岸局势困扰 ■</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 22:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</guid></item><item><title>为了所有以色列人的利益，废除排他性民族国家法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</guid></item><item><title>感谢以色列极右翼财政部长，我们正处于经济灾难的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/thanks-to-israels-far-right-finance-minister-were-on-the-brink-of-economic-disaster/0000018b-fdb9-de0a-a18f-fffd61100000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/thanks-to-israels-far-right-finance-minister-were-on-the-brink-of-economic-disaster/0000018b-fdb9-de0a-a18f-fffd61100000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的胜利不是我们的胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-victory-is-not-our-victory/0000018b-fd72-de0a-a18f-ff7714300000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-victory-is-not-our-victory/0000018b-fd72-de0a-a18f-ff7714300000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔正在嘲笑内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-is-making-laughingstock-out-of-netanyahu/0000018b-fd72-d99b-a7eb-fdf6152d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-is-making-laughingstock-out-of-netanyahu/0000018b-fd72-d99b-a7eb-fdf6152d0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》如何统计 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件中以色列的死亡人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-haaretz-is-counting-israels-dead-from-the-october-7-hamas-attack/0000018b-d42c-d423-affb-f7afe1a70000</link><description>以下是对 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中以色列死难者名单的完整记录，记录了我们在新闻报道上一丝不苟、令人心力交瘁的过程：</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 20:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-haaretz-is-counting-israels-dead-from-the-october-7-hamas-attack/0000018b-d42c-d423-affb-f7afe1a70000</guid></item><item><title>“我们可以睡觉而不用担心死亡”：停火为加沙人带来了新鲜空气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/we-can-sleep-without-fear-of-dying-cease-fire-is-a-breath-of-fresh-air-for-gazans/0000018b-fd98-de73-a9bb-ffff81ec0000</link><description>虽然只是暂时的，但加沙居民热切地等待四天的战斗暂停，并希望这将为更长的喘息时间打开大门。 “在我们每天都处于死亡状态的一个半月之后，这是乐观的迹象——生命的迹象。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 20:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/we-can-sleep-without-fear-of-dying-cease-fire-is-a-breath-of-fresh-air-for-gazans/0000018b-fd98-de73-a9bb-ffff81ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通讯部长威胁国土报，建议惩罚其加沙战争报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/israels-communications-minister-threatens-haaretz-suggests-penalizing-its-war-coverage/0000018b-fd0c-de73-a9bb-ffefb9f10000</link><description>在利库德集团部长什洛莫·卡希提议对《国土报》进行经济处罚后，他称之为“谎言、失败主义宣传”，著名记者猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列新闻自由的最新攻击</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 18:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/israels-communications-minister-threatens-haaretz-suggests-penalizing-its-war-coverage/0000018b-fd0c-de73-a9bb-ffefb9f10000</guid></item><item><title>“作为四个男孩的以色列母亲，军队游戏不是我想玩的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：战争愈演愈烈，一位母亲担心孩子的未来，一对俄罗斯夫妇逃离另一个冲突地区</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>导致灾难的不是加沙脱离接触，而是内塔尼亚胡的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</link><description>追寻10月7日惨案的历史根源，我们必须回到十年前总理的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官：加沙“处于医疗灾难的边缘”，有疾病爆发的迹象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</link><description>几位接受《国土报》采访的外交官报告称，近东救济工程处警告称，儿童皮肤病爆发，胃肠道疾病病例有所增加。一位外交官警告说，加沙的医疗系统正在崩溃。 “如果发生这种情况，以色列也会受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</guid></item></channel></rss>